data.description: Gorgeous home!!! This is truly a spectacular 3 bedroom 2.5 bath home with an inviting long foyer, super bright with lots of windows, easy to maintain with warm colored tile throughout the home. Kitchen features granite counter tops, a breakfast bar, and a large pantry. The kitchen also opens to the spacious family room making entertaining enjoyable! Out back is where you will love to spend your weekends grilling under the patio and relaxing in the back yard. This home includes a storage shed and much more.
